lead_paragraph: The U.S. says the disappearance of five Hong Kong residents associated with a publisher specializing in books banned in mainland China raises serious questions about Beijing's commitments to the territory's autonomy.

headline.main: US Concerned Over Disappearance of 5 Hong Kong Residents
